page.title: 11Housing in Leamington Spa.
page.content: There are many types of housing in Leamington Spa, Leamington is most famous for its regency architecture. All Saints'School carried out a survey involving several estate agents.We found the most popular type of housing in the area is a three bedroomed semi_detached house. The normal price for a three bedroomed Semi_detached house is about 30,000.We also found that the most popular district to live in Lillington.Lillington was found the most popular place to live because of its good housing and house prices.
